  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 86211e2fd74fb484598c1176279aee61, type: 3}
  m_Name: Chef Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueColor: {r: 0.3490566, g: 0.31706628, b: 0.28484336, a: 1}
  startingNode:
    dialogueText: Please, take a seat, sir. Your food will be served very soon.
    characterEmotion: 1
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018021
    - rid: 5324356914828018026
    - rid: 5324356914828018038
    isRootNode: 1
    editorPosition: {x: 300, y: 200}
    guid:
      Part1: 2187425879
      Part2: 1303396138
      Part3: 822268818
      Part4: 3030757262
    tag: 
  allNodes:
  - dialogueText: 
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 1
    editorPosition: {x: 300, y: 200}
    guid:
      Part1: 2187425879
      Part2: 1303396138
      Part3: 822268818
      Part4: 3030757262
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Emphasis on "the", I would say. I doubt you''re going to find
      anyone who''s even remotely at my level in these parts.

      Which, to be
      fair, is less of a compliment to myself and more of an insult to this barren
      wasteland of a tundra.'
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018023
    - rid: 5324356914828018024
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1187, y: -184.87875}
    guid:
      Part1: 3602120331
      Part2: 1166060994
      Part3: 911281044
      Part4: 2523521365
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: Oh... why, yes, it is. I guess I must have left it here when I...
      saw her...
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018029
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1123.8, y: 242.00002}
    guid:
      Part1: 2281328821
      Part2: 1083067839
      Part3: 430758297
      Part4: 2381979112
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'My...*sigh*... ex-wife... the guest sitting over there.

      It''s
      been years since I last saw her, and we didn''t really... end in good terms,
      if you get me.'
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018031
    - rid: 5324356914828018032
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2000, y: 270}
    guid:
      Part1: 3527085235
      Part2: 1194001365
      Part3: 4028895926
      Part4: 1884205132
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: '...yes. And, unlike what people seem to believe, it''s not because
      of her fortune or my debt with her for allowing me to follow my career.

      I
      genuinely do still love her, and though I know she might not reciprocate, I
      am unable to forget how I was when i was with her... *sigh* '
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018034
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3009.2275, y: 115.00003}
    guid:
      Part1: 1137026615
      Part2: 1229502098
      Part3: 998843818
      Part4: 3463862481
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Resent her? She single-handedly financed my career as a chef and
      gave me years of unconditional love.

      Even if I didn''t still love her
      (which I do), I have a debt with her that i doubt I''ll ever be able to pay...
      *sigh*'
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses: []
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 3071.3, y: 320.00006}
    guid:
      Part1: 2235048724
      Part2: 1328629158
      Part3: 2450035843
      Part4: 3288955765
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "WHAT? Of course I wouldn't, what makes you say that?\nEver since
      <b>that incident</b> with our boss, its use has been strictly forbidden...
      \nin fact, only hotel workers should be able to access it, so, where did you
      find it?"
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018037
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2619, y: -176}
    guid:
      Part1: 1832242742
      Part2: 1121443926
      Part3: 2250865802
      Part4: 3781854202
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "Oh, I feel so sorry for her. \nShe seems to have found an ill-intended
      <b>note</b> on a room threatening her.\nWhoever felt the need to do something
      so cruel wasn't even brave enough to sign..."
    characterEmotion: 0
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828018040
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1381.0895, y: 525}
    guid:
      Part1: 2099377356
      Part2: 1175523789
      Part3: 1618177925
      Part4: 73563290
    tag: 
